msgid ""
"A powerful, free donation and payment widget that allows your visitors to "
"support you via credit card or cryptocurrency (Quai). No monthly fees, no "
"third-party subscriptions – just your wallet and free services."
msgstr ""
"Magna, libera dona et paymentum widget qui visitatores tuos permittit te "
"sustinere per tarxiam credituum aut cryptocurrency (Quai). Nihil mensis "
"sumptus, nihil subscriptionum tertii partis – solum tua porta et libera "
"servitia."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Nonnulli naviatores scripts tertiae partis ob privatum restringunt. Hoc "
"proxy scripts per servum tuum transferre ut has obstructions transigat."

